#: templates/welcome.html:39
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                You play squash, tennis or paddel? Or may be chess, darts or "
"pool? But you can't find partners? This is %(QWIK)sGAME! Now finding "
"partners and arranging games is fast and easy. With %(QWIK)sGAME you have "
"all match invitations in one place. Just pick one or post your own.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Anda bermain skuasy, tenis atau padel? Atau mungkin catur, "
"darts atau pool? Tetapi sukar mencari rakan bermain? Inilah %(QWIK)sGAME! "
"Kini mencari rakan dan mengatur permainan menjadi cepat dan mudah. Dengan "
"%(QWIK)sGAME anda mempunyai semua jemputan perlawanan di satu tempat. "
"Pilih sahaja satu atau hantar jemputan anda sendiri.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:45
msgid "Organize A Match For Free!"
msgstr "Atur Perlawanan Secara Percuma!"

