#: templates/welcome.html:245
msgid "FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS"
msgstr "SOALAN LAZIM"

#: templates/welcome.html:248
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                What is %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Apakah %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:255
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME is an app which facilitates finding "
"partners and arranging 2-player games.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME ialah aplikasi yang memudahkan pencarian "
"rakan bermain dan pengaturan permainan 2 pemain.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:262
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                For which games can I find partners on %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Untuk permainan apa saya boleh mencari rakan di %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:269
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME focuses on 2-player games only with "
"ambitious plans for multi-player games in the future. Currently we have the "
"most popular 2-player games like tennis, squash, table tennis, badminton, "
"racquetball, but also chess, darts, backgammon, billiards and more.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME memberi tumpuan kepada permainan 2 pemain "
"sahaja dengan rancangan besar untuk permainan berbilang pemain pada masa "
"hadapan. Kini kami mempunyai permainan 2 pemain yang popular seperti tenis, "
"skuasy, ping pong, badminton, racquetball, serta catur, dart, backgammon, "
"biliard dan banyak lagi.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:276
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Is %(QWIK)sGAME paid?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Adakah %(QWIK)sGAME berbayar?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:283
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME is free of charge.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME adalah percuma.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:290
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Is %(QWIK)sGAME available in my country?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Adakah %(QWIK)sGAME tersedia di negara saya?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:297
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME works anywhere in the world.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME boleh digunakan di mana-mana sahaja di dunia.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:304
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                How do I find partner and schedule a match with "
"%(QWIK)sGAME?\n"
msgstr ""

#: templates/welcome.html:311
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    To find a partner and organize a match start by sending "
"an invitation for a match. Select the game, venue and a timeframe. It is "
"recommended to call the venue and check if there are available playgrounds "
"for your preferred timeframe. Your Match Invitation will be visible in the "
"QWIKFeed to other Players. Multiple Players may respond to your Invitation. "
"You get to choose the best offer and confirm the match. You can also reply "
"to an existing invitation from the %(QWIK)sFeed by placing an offer for a "
"particular hour from the given timeframe.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    Untuk mencari rakan dan mengatur perlawanan, mulakan "
"dengan menghantar jemputan perlawanan. Pilih permainan, lokasi dan jangka "
"masa. Adalah disyorkan untuk menghubungi lokasi dan menyemak sama ada "
"terdapat gelanggang yang tersedia untuk jangka masa pilihan anda. "
"Jemputan Perlawanan anda akan kelihatan di QWIKFeed kepada Pemain lain. "
"Beberapa Pemain mungkin membalas jemputan anda. Anda boleh memilih tawaran "
"terbaik dan mengesahkan perlawanan. Anda juga boleh membalas jemputan yang "
"sedia ada daripada %(QWIK)sFeed dengan membuat tawaran untuk jam tertentu "
"dalam jangka masa yang diberikan.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:318
msgid ""
"\n"
"                How many invitations can I send?\n"
msgstr ""

#: templates/welcome.html:325
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    You can post as many invitations as you wish every day "
"and for any game, venue or timeframe.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    Anda boleh menyiarkan sebanyak mana jemputan yang anda "
"inginkan setiap hari untuk sebarang permainan, lokasi atau jangka masa.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:332
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                What is %(QWIK)sFeed?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Apakah %(QWIK)sFeed?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:339
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    You can find all current invitations in our "
"%(QWIK)sFeed. It is contantly updated with new invitations sent by Players.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    Anda boleh menemui semua jemputan semasa di "
"%(QWIK)sFeed kami. Ia sentiasa dikemas kini dengan jemputan baharu yang "
"dihantar oleh Pemain.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:346
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Who books the court/playground?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Siapa yang menempah gelanggang/tempat bermain?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:353
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    The Player who send the initial match invitation is "
"responsible to call and book a court/playground once the match is confirmed. "
"The Player is also recommended to call and check the venue availability "
"before sending the invitation.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    Pemain yang menghantar jemputan perlawanan awal "
"bertanggungjawab untuk menghubungi dan menempah gelanggang/tempat bermain "
"apabila perlawanan telah disahkan. Pemain juga disyorkan untuk menghubungi "
"dan menyemak ketersediaan lokasi sebelum menghantar jemputan.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:360
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Why can't I find %(QWIK)sGAME in the PlayStore and "
"AppStore?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Mengapa saya tidak dapat menemui %(QWIK)sGAME di PlayStore "
"dan AppStore?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:367
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME is a Progressive Web App. It's the new "
"generation of apps. No need to download nor install anything. Just save "
"%(QWIK)sGAME on your Home screen. %(QWIK)sGAME PWA works on all operating "
"systems and an Internet Browser is the only requirement.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME ialah Progressive Web App. Ia adalah "
"generasi baharu aplikasi. Tidak perlu memuat turun atau memasang apa-apa. "
"Hanya simpan %(QWIK)sGAME pada skrin utama anda. %(QWIK)sGAME PWA berfungsi "
"pada semua sistem operasi dan hanya memerlukan pelayar internet.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:374
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Who owns %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Siapakah pemilik %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:381
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME is managed by QWIKGAME Inc. registered in "
"Victoria, Australia as a Not For Profit Association. All discussions and "
"decisions regarding %(QWIK)sGAME are made online in the <a href=\"https://"
"forum.qwikgame.org/\" target=\"_blank\">QWIK Forum</a>. Your assistance will "
"be most welcome.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME diuruskan oleh QWIKGAME Inc. yang "
"berdaftar di Victoria, Australia sebagai Persatuan Bukan Untung. Semua "
"perbincangan dan keputusan berkaitan %(QWIK)sGAME dibuat secara dalam talian "
"di <a href=\"https://forum.qwikgame.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Forum QWIK</a>. "
"Bantuan anda amat dialu-alukan.\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:388
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Is %(QWIK)sGAME open-source?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Adakah %(QWIK)sGAME sumber terbuka?\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:395
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    Yes! The %(QWIK)sGAME software is entirely open-source. "
"The latest code can be found on %(github_link)s. Your assistance will be "
"most welcome.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    Ya! Perisian %(QWIK)sGAME adalah sepenuhnya sumber "
"terbuka. Kod terkini boleh didapati di %(github_link)s. Bantuan anda amat "
"dialu-alukan.\n"

